description: MATTHIEU then turns the tables and shows us that the mostaccomplished fisting bottoms make superlative fisting tops. MARClies on his back, legs wide open, offering up his hungry, talented holeto MATTHIEU, the master. And master MARC's hole he does,swimming the breath stroke, one hand in, then the other, stretchingwider and wider, tempting MARC to take both of his nimble hands.Not to be outdone in the rosebud department, MARC is eager toshow off his own wide, hot rose, which MATTHIEU appreciates withhis willing tongue.
title: Fistpack 10 - Best In Hole
